Visit recipes.com.au for recipe inspiration. Deconstructed Banoffee Pie Skill Level: EasyPrep time: 20 min (plus assembly)Serves: 4 Ingredients: 300mL thickened cream1 tbsp caster sugar1 tsp vanilla bean paste395g can Nestle Top 'n' Fill Caramel125g buttersnap biscuits, crushed 2 bananas, peeled and sliced 2 tbsp toasted coconut chips Method: 1. In a bowl, add thickened cream, sugar and vanilla bean paste. Beat with an electric mixer, until thickened. Spoon into a large piping bag fitted with a 1cm round nozzle. 2. In a medium bowl whisk Nestle Top n' Fill Caramel until smooth.3. In 4 stemless wine glasses, evenly fill glasses with crushed biscuits, followed by Nestle Top 'n' Fill Caramel, bananas and whipped cream. Keep layering evenly until all ingredients are used and your last layer is the whipped thickened cream from step 1. 4. Refrigerate for 1 hour or until chilled. Top with toasted coconut.

Cheesy Corn Dip Recipe

250g Light Cream Cheese
1/4 cup Grated Tasty Cheese
150mL Light Sour Cream
250g MasterFoods™ Corn Relish

product.name: Doritos Hot Salsa
product.description:
Add a Flavourful Mexican-Inspired Kick the Right Way
Perfect for your Doritos to Dip and Crunch, this hot Salsa will wildly enhance any of your tortilla corn chips and elevate them to platter-worthy status. Best of all, our punchy, tangy Mexican-inspired flavours contain absolutely no artificial colours or flavours and are suitable even for vegetarians.

Ideal to Pair with Tortilla and Corn Chips
Just like how our Doritos corn chips are carefully put together for maximum scooping and dipping efficiency, our Hot Salsa is a Mexican-inspired dip experience that’ll go perfectly atop any corn chip. Our salsa sauce combines explosive and spicy Mexican-inspired flavours with undertones of mellow and tangy tomatoes to keep you reaching into the jar.

Tailor-made for Entertaining
Add that extra oomph of flavour to your next snack spread, whether it's for your next party or family gathering. Grab one of our Doritos Mild Salsa dips along with our Doritos Hot Salsa Dip to ensure there’s options for everyone. Load up your Doritos Corn Chips or Crackers with our spicy tangy salsa so you and your guests can enjoy the boldest of snacking experiences. They’re the perfect entertaining size to stick in the centre of the platter.

Ideal for Entertaining Anyone and Everyone
Despite our explosive and in-your-face flavour, Doritos Hot Salsa contains absolutely no artificial colours or flavours. Just like our corn chips, you can add Doritos Hot Salsa to your meal to give it that extra kick of spice or flavour. Simply scoop some on top of your nachos to add a flavourful kick to your weekly Mexican night or Nachos night.
Scoop up some of our other recipes here:
https://doritos.com.au/meal-hacks-doritos-recipes

The jars used as Doritos Hot Salsa packaging are recyclable. Check with your local council recycling guidelines to dispose of your waste correctly and thoughtfully.


Country of Origin: Made in United Kingdom

Start your day the Aussie way with VEGEMITE! 
 
VEGEMITE is more than just a spread; it's a national icon that has been bringing smiles to Australian faces since 1923. Made from a unique blend of brewers' yeast extract and enriched with essential B vitamins, VEGEMITE is a powerhouse of nutrition and flavour. 
 
Taste the Tradition: VEGEMITE's rich, savoury taste is a beloved staple in Australian households. Its bold, umami flavour, with a hint of saltiness, is perfect for those who crave a distinctive and satisfying taste experience. Spread it thinly on buttered toast for a classic breakfast or add it to your favourite sandwich for an extra burst of flavour. 
 
Versatility at Its Best: VEGEMITE isn't just for toast. Its versatility makes it a secret ingredient in many recipes. Use it to enhance the flavour of soups, stews, and marinades, or pair it with cheese and avocado for a delicious twist. The possibilities are endless! 
 
Health Benefits: Packed with B vitamins, VEGEMITE supports your overall well-being. Thiamin (B1) is essential for brain function, riboflavin (B2) supports your nervous system, niacin (B3) aids in energy release, and folate helps fight fatigue. Enjoy VEGEMITE as part of a balanced, varied diet and active lifestyle. 
 
A True Aussie Icon: Proudly owned and made in Australia, VEGEMITE embodies the spirit of the nation. Its rich history and unique taste make it a symbol of Australian culture and heritage. Whether you're a lifelong fan or trying it for the first time, VEGEMITE is sure to bring a touch of Aussie pride to your table. 
 
Discover the delicious and nutritious world of VEGEMITE today.

product.description:
For temporary relief of sore throats. Always read the label and follow the directions for use.


Strepsils Sore Throat Relief Orange soothes throat discomfort and provides double antibacterial action.

Uses
- For fast, soothing and effective relief from the discomfort of sore throats and minor mouth infections. 
- Contains two antibacterial agents to help kill bacteria that can cause sore throats and mouth infections.


Active Ingredients

  • Dichlorobenzyl Alcohol 1.2mg
  • Amylmetacresol 600micrograms.

Directions

- Suitable for adults and children over 6 years.
- Dissolve one lozenge slowly in mouth every 2 to 3 hours as required.

- Do not use if foil seal is broken.

Store below 25°C.

Product Warnings

- Not suitable for children 6 years and under.
- If symptoms persist consult your doctor.
- Keep all medicines out of reach of children.
- Contains: Each lozenge contains sugars (sucrose & glucose).

product.description:
Gluten-Free Crackers Perfect for the Lunch Box
Sakata Rice Crackers are versatile and delicious. Pack them with cheese in your kid’s school lunch box, enjoy them with your favourite dip, or eat them straight from the packet for a pleasurable snacking experience. Sakata Plain Rice Crackers are the perfect, rice snack the whole family can enjoy.

Subtle Flavours with Rich Origin
The Sakata rice crackers are snacks of Japanese origin. The original "usuyaki" crispy rice cracker was first created in the Japanese village of Sakata. 

At the centre of Japanese cuisine is the art of simplicity - a few ingredients skilfully combined to achieve a simple, unpretentious result. At Sakata we will always start with the highest quality ingredients, artfully crafting them into delicious rice snacks we hope you will love.

A Perfect Base for your Favourite Flavours
Our plain crackers pair amicably with any of your favourite toppings, from cheese to smoked salmon. That’s why our gluten-free rice crackers are tailor-made for entertaining.

• Three natural ingredients (rice (97%), rice bran oil, salt) creating our signature cracker flavour
• No artificial colour or flavours
• Gluten-free snack
• Rice biscuits with 102 calories per serve
